15
00:01:25,415 --> 00:01:30,817
And he was one of the worst of all, could not be killed.

16
00:01:32,870 --> 00:01:36,999
So Shiva and Parvati were married

17
00:01:37,082 --> 00:01:42,300
for this special purpose to produce this powerful Shaktiputra,

18
00:01:42,331 --> 00:01:46,452
means the son of the Shakti, known as Kartikeya.

19
00:01:48,337 --> 00:01:51,899
And He was just born to kill this horrible devil,

20
00:01:53,475 --> 00:01:54,835
called as Narakasura.

21
00:01:56,041 --> 00:02:00,800
And He killed. That is the day, fourteenth day.

22
00:02:01,349 --> 00:02:03,349
It is something like Halloween, that day.

23
00:02:04,027 --> 00:02:06,027
Because that is the day they opened

24
00:02:06,571 --> 00:02:13,152
the gates of hell and put all the devils into hell.

25
00:02:13,592 --> 00:02:19,472
And that’s why that day one has to rest in the morning time as long as possible.

26
00:02:19,722 --> 00:02:23,322
So that let all the devils be put in nicely

27
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:27,689
because some of them might be hanging around still.

28
00:02:28,349 --> 00:02:31,539
It’s better to allow them to get out.

29
00:02:32,083 --> 00:02:34,562
I mean in the realm that you are

