00:03:01,369 --> 00:03:03,458
people celebrated.

38
00:03:03,557 --> 00:03:08,633
That celebration is expressed next day,

39
00:03:08,778 --> 00:03:13,320
which that day is the day of Diwali they say.

40
00:03:13,359 --> 00:03:17,283
That is the day they also worship Lakshmi, because

41
00:03:18,158 --> 00:03:20,632
they think that

